<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Written_by_Ibn_Tumart">Written by Ibn Tumart</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ibn_Tumart&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13" title="Edit section: Written by Ibn Tumart"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
